<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="take-sth-into-consideration">take sth into consideration</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>考虑到某事；顾及某事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We will take your recent illness into consideration when marking your exams.
在给你的考卷打分时，我们会考虑到你近期生病的因素。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I would appreciate it if you could take my proposal into consideration.
如果您能考虑我的建议，我将不胜感激。</p><footer>2015 上海书面表达</footer></div></div>